{"tid":1455020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場手足 我地唔可以再少一個人！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:29.000Z","uid":106671,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"696f7ed1575d16fe27fb1b3c0a4ad7873315a566","tid":1455020,"uid":106671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"機場員工表示<br />\n今晚有機放催淚<br />\n飛機升降 開始 控制 <br />\n6點 只有 起飛 降落 加埋得 40班 <br />\n9點 就 起飛 降落 減到 只得 30班<br />\n警琴晚開始已經不停運gear入去<br />\n警都不停入緊去<br />\n<br />\n(我空姐同事)<br />\n<br />\n傳出去 我一手 <br />\n我而加係TPE 地勤話消息講香港機場成個封左到今晚12點無機升降<br />\n並唔係限制重新編排<br />\n唔知係咪想等到無遊客清場<br />\n<br />\nfact checked<br />\nAA sent message to all airline management.<br />\n今天餘下所有航班取消<br />\n已從外站起飛嘅航班有機會未能於香港國際機場降落<br />\n而未起飛嘅亦唔會俾clearance走<br />\n<br />\n目標已達，小心tg"},{"pid":"0e56e9167c7e701d48027a8a74769211f6ca3c4c","tid":1455020,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n<br />\n機場T1 抵港大堂疏散路線<br />\n-<br />\n藍線為大路，有機會被警察部防封鎖。<br />\n紅線為緊急逃生路線，已查証可繼續通行。<br />\n切記不要進入禁區，如需要出示passport及boarding pass的地方，因機場特警係可以合理執法。<br />\n<br />\n#現場情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20UmC1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20UmC1c.jpg&h=3544e0a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"125c39c5d8d28f68694d7b6088d51544edb4db10","tid":1455020,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85c4d0b6b68a18db8061bd492cea98ba50efd41","tid":1455020,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"又係想冇旅客就圍，走呀大家，恢復番先再去坐過"},{"pid":"88541892b5bdbc4d8bc62dbf612629b30e6ef32b","tid":1455020,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}